{"tid":1828189,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［文青末日］黨媒聯同小粉紅，迫香港誠品歸邊","createTime":"2020-01-17T14:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T00:06:44.000Z","uid":101315,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"372f56d8c926e16ef1ed0db066c18248ce938cea","tid":1828189,"uid":101315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T14:51:17.000Z","msg":"早幾日有中国人在微博篤灰，指責香港誠品在當眼地方擺賣反共及港獨書籍，並呼籲杯葛誠品在中国的分店：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSGbCoW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSGbCoW.jpg&h=f7caaab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n涉事書籍包括何清漣的《紅色滲透》、余杰的《香港獨立》、以及徐承恩的《香港，鬱躁的家邦》和《思索家邦》。<br />\n<br />\n然後《文匯報》好爽手，第二日就出左篇報導：<a href=\"http://news.wenweipo.com/2020/01/15/IN2001150080.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.wenweipo.com%2F2020%2F01%2F15%2FIN2001150080.htm&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKO9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=2a7d9ae1\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.wenweipo.com/2020/01/15/IN2001150080.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n【文匯網訊】有網友昨日(14日)在社交媒體爆料，稱台灣品牌書店「誠品生活」，一邊在內地大量開店，一邊在香港大賣港毒書籍。<br />\n<br />\n據香港中通社報道，誠品書店的香港店面不僅將大量港毒書籍擺放在店內醒目位置，並且這些播毒的書籍隔壁就是兒童區，其用心「不言而喻」。<br />\n<br />\n截止發稿，誠品書店暫時未有就事件做出回應。<br />\n<br />\n昨天下午，根據網友「來點石錘」在社交媒體發帖爆料，稱香港一家誠品書店在醒目位置擺放了多本港毒書籍，如《香港X立》、《香港，郁躁的XX》，單看書名就知其中內容。<br />\n<br />\n其中《香港X立》一書特別顯眼，封面上還畫著2019年的反修例示威遊行中暴徒的經典裝扮：黃色安全帽、護目鏡、口罩和雨傘。<br />\n<br />\n帖子還有聊天截圖，指「香港書店賣的大部分書都是抹黑的，之前只以為言論自由，沒想到這麼大禍，太大意了&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n據了解，這些港毒書籍不僅實體店有售，網上誠品書店也在銷售中。<br />\n<br />\n誠品書店是一家台灣書店品牌。2012年8月11日，誠品書店在島外的第一間分店香港銅鑼灣店開幕，目前在香港已有三家分店。<br />\n<br />\n而從2015年11月開始，誠品書店開始了其在大陸的佈局，蘇州分店是其在大陸設立的第一家旗艦店。目前，在搜索引擎上能找到多家大陸分店。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URHRCqR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURHRCqR.jpg&h=0c2ba977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本就想迫誠品自我審查。令人憂慮的是，誠品個底本身唔算硬淨。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94bf640e6c16564feb8c4e52f0f19f190b77f6ba","tid":1828189,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T14:52:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">求下大家<br />\n歐美議員日日講野無人理<br />\n今日好多鬧華為鬧中共tweet響task2呀 <br />\n幫手啦上唔到千呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKO9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=eccb2934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"0101d574835920344c852c51e7aab80253189fd1","tid":1828189,"uid":73959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T14:57:49.000Z","msg":"偽文青: wfc我ig啲相色tone一樣就得了"},{"pid":"99eadcb10c3aa0a21f56803d79fdac42d2b5efd3","tid":1828189,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T16:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb072e53fe73325722eef7470fa067ce5084c7f","tid":1828189,"uid":185121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T22:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港誠品唔係一咗跪咗㗎啦咩?本身已經唔多反共書㗎啦喎, 咁都有得逼歸邊"},{"pid":"41b2c90ce60fa14786c93699a72ac126e673edd5","tid":1828189,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T00:06:44.000Z","msg":"香港X立<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文匪賤蓄係咪獨立會好似講粗口咁打冷震？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj